    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3143710/extras/f2e2f2a4ed934f23cbf7a1063fdd83ae.avif?t=1770900894\" width=1560 height=244 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在《PUBG: Blindspot》中，视野就是策略的核心。通过俯视视角观察每一个角度，抢占你的战术优势。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >视野控制是赢下每一场战斗的关键所在。提前发现每一个转角之后的隐藏变数。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一处角度的处理是否得当，将会改变整场战斗的走势。观察、确认、预判。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3143710/extras/18c66639c4d596dbb0815641b3b7e654.poster.avif?t=1770900894\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3143710/extras/18c66639c4d596dbb0815641b3b7e654.webm?t=1770900894\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3143710/extras/18c66639c4d596dbb0815641b3b7e654.mp4?t=1770900894\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>战术协同：</strong>要在5v5战斗中取得胜利，需要密切的配合行动和巧妙的职业选择。每名玩家都会在战斗中履行独特的职责，拥有自己鲜明的定位，并且能以自己的力量影响战斗走势。你的团队构成和阅读战场的能力将会重新定义每一次遭遇。运用巧妙的策略互相支援，与你的队友协同合作，带领你的队伍走向胜利。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3143710/extras/073f8d665a0500dee5db8f284288cf68.poster.avif?t=1770900894\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3143710/extras/073f8d665a0500dee5db8f284288cf68.webm?t=1770900894\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3143710/extras/073f8d665a0500dee5db8f284288cf68.mp4?t=1770900894\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>共享视野战斗：</strong>游戏的视野系统会实时分享每一名玩家的视线，可以让玩家们立刻发现敌人，制定路线策略，选择高风险的打法。扩大你的视野，才能抢占策略上风，支配战斗的节奏。展现你的战斗风采，帮助你的队伍占据视野优势，拿下胜利！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3143710/extras/765fc52b3ab39342663811874d769153.poster.avif?t=1770900894\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3143710/extras/765fc52b3ab39342663811874d769153.webm?t=1770900894\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3143710/extras/765fc52b3ab39342663811874d769153.mp4?t=1770900894\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>全新形态的战术射击：</strong>游戏的战斗将提供快节奏的中近距离射击体验，并融合速度和策略元素。紧凑的交战距离，巧妙利用掩体，以及精确的角度控制等玩法将会提供远超只是扣下扳机射击的游戏深度。每一次观察、每一次转身、每一条视线都是能够起到决定性作用的战术选择，将每一次遭遇都升级为一场对决。</p>",
